CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 3, 1962, pg. C3, reads: "Photos of Your Pittsburgh Story Rally - Chatting - Shown are (left to right) Courier Religious Editor B. H. Logan, Bishop Gomez and the Rev. H. V. Eberhardt, of Brown Chapel AME Church. - All Photos by Harris."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of B. H. Logan, Bishop Joseph Gomez, and Rev. H. V. Eberhardt, posed in Soldiers and Sailors Memorial Hall, for Pittsburgh Courier Newspaper's Appreciation Day Rally
